Remember the other day you were saying...?

00:08:01.810 --> 00:08:04.450
This better be real, Takumi!

00:08:04.450 --> 00:08:08.970
If this turns out to be a joke... you'll be sorry!

00:08:10.020 --> 00:08:13.320
Are you sure she's bringing her friend?

00:08:13.320 --> 00:08:14.820
Don't worry...

00:08:14.820 --> 00:08:19.360
Mogi said she was bringing her friend.

00:08:19.360 --> 00:08:23.160
I wonder if she's cute... or has a nice body...

00:08:23.160 --> 00:08:27.170
...or maybe she is beautiful!

00:08:27.170 --> 00:08:30.870
I think she is Mogi's junior high school friend.

00:08:30.870 --> 00:08:33.910
As long as she is decent-looking...

00:08:33.910 --> 00:08:37.810
I shouldn't expect too much...

00:08:37.810 --> 00:08:42.020
I can't believe you kept your promise, Takumi!

00:08:42.020 --> 00:08:45.350
I'm so lucky to have a good friend like you...

00:08:45.350 --> 00:08:46.890
It's nothing, really...

00:08:46.890 --> 00:08:52.160
I'll be the best racer at Mount Akina
with a pretty girl in my arms.

00:08:55.160 --> 00:09:01.000
Not on my Levin, you darn pigeons!

00:09:01.000 --> 00:09:03.640
They should be here by now...

00:09:03.640 --> 00:09:05.200
Hey!

00:09:06.210 --> 00:09:07.440
Were you waiting long?

00:09:07.440 --> 00:09:09.980
--Don't do that, Mogi!
--Hi.

00:09:09.980 --> 00:09:15.380
Itsuki, this is my friend Saori.
Saori, this is Takumi and Itsuki.

00:09:18.350 --> 00:09:20.150
Nice meeting you.

00:09:20.150 --> 00:09:21.780
You, too.

00:09:24.990 --> 00:09:27.480
She's... very pretty...

00:09:32.870 --> 00:09:35.670
So you are a street racer?

00:09:35.670 --> 00:09:39.740
Well, I belong to a team
called the Akina Speed Stars,

00:09:39.740 --> 00:09:43.840
and I'm the third or fourth fastest...

00:09:43.840 --> 00:09:48.320
I'm well known in Gunma
as "Levin of Mount Akina."

00:09:48.320 --> 00:09:49.550
Pretty cool!

00:09:49.550 --> 00:09:51.650
What's a street racer?

00:09:51.650 --> 00:09:54.890
What, you really don't know?

00:09:54.890 --> 00:09:56.520
A street racer is a...

00:09:56.520 --> 00:10:00.190
<i>Oh, man! She's far beyond my expectations!</i>

00:10:00.190 --> 00:10:02.250
Watch out, Itsuki!

00:10:09.870 --> 00:10:12.710
--Want me to drive?
--No, I got it.

00:10:12.710 --> 00:10:16.270
Sorry, a street racer's bad habit...

00:10:29.120 --> 00:10:31.130
Feeling okay?

00:10:31.130 --> 00:10:33.620
I'm fine...

00:10:35.960 --> 00:10:38.430
He drives kind of rough...

00:10:38.430 --> 00:10:41.730
Hey! Takumi and Natsuki!

00:10:43.040 --> 00:10:45.470
Look at us!

00:10:45.470 --> 00:10:47.940
Why don't you join us?

00:10:51.250 --> 00:10:53.810
They do look good together.

00:10:53.810 --> 00:10:55.440
Yeah...

